timing_librar...socv_from_aocv(25.10)    timing_librar...socv_from_aocv(25.10)

Name
       timing_library_infer_socv_from_aocv

Syntax
       timing_library_infer_socv_from_aocv {true | false}

       Default: false

       Controls the transformation of AOCV data.

       This  global  variable infers sensitivity data from AOCV libraries, and
       must be set before loading any timing library data.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

